{"ja330:0.1":"Jataka ","ja330:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","ja330:0.3":"Kutidusakavagga ","ja330:0.4":"10. Silavimamsajataka ","ja330:1.1":"“Silam kireva kalyanam, ","ja330:1.2":"silam loke anuttaram; ","ja330:1.3":"Passa ghoraviso nago, ","ja330:1.4":"silavati na hannati”. ","ja330:2.1":"“Yavadevassahu kinci, ","ja330:2.2":"tavadeva akhadisum; ","ja330:2.3":"Sangamma kulala loke, ","ja330:2.4":"na himsanti akincanam. ","ja330:3.1":"Sukham nirasa supati, ","ja330:3.2":"asa phalavati sukha; ","ja330:3.3":"Asam nirasam katvana, ","ja330:3.4":"sukham supati pingala. ","ja330:4.1":"Na samadhiparo atthi, ","ja330:4.2":"asmim loke paramhi ca; ","ja330:4.3":"Na param napi attanam, ","ja330:4.4":"vihimsati samahito”ti. ","ja330:5.1":"Silavimamsajatakam dasamam. ","ja330:5.2":"Kutidusakavaggo tatiyo. ","ja330:6.1":"Tassuddanam ","ja330:7.1":"Samanussa saduddubha yacanako, ","ja330:7.2":"Atha mendavaruttama godhavaro; ","ja330:7.3":"Atha kayasakepuka bhotivaro, ","ja330:7.4":"Atha radhasusilavarena dasati. "}